l\u00f3gico: La acupuntura puede ayudar a fortalecer el sistema inmunol\u00f3gico al estimular la producci\u00f3n de c\u00e9lulas blancas de la sangre. Esto puede ser especialmente beneficioso para las personas que tienen un sistema inmunol\u00f3gico debilitado debido a enfermedades o tratamientos m\u00e9dicos.\nCarlos Nicolas Ladr\u00f3n de Guevara Lecourtois", "language": null, "image": "https://acid.la/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ACUPUNTURA-PORTADA.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#qodef-page-content", "https://acid.la/", "https://acid.la/category/espiritualidades/", "https://acid.la/category/tendencixs/", "https://acid.la/category/gaming/", "https://acid.la/category/b3-yours3lf/", "https://acid.la/category/showbiz/", "https://acid.la/category/gen-z/", "#", "https://acid.la/category/techhhh/", "https://acid.la/category/actualidad/", "https://acid.la/category/kulture/", "https://acid.la/category/im-ok/", "https://acid.la/category/acid-magazine/", "https://acid.la/category/jijiji-jajaja/", "https://acid.la/", "https://acid.la/category/espiritualidades/", "https://acid.la/category/tendencixs/", "https://acid.la/category/gaming/", "https://acid.la/category/b3-yours3lf/", "https://acid.la/category/showbiz/", "https://acid.la/category/gen-z/", "#", "https://acid.la/category/techhhh/", "https://acid.la/category/actualidad/", "https://acid.la/category/kulture/", "https://acid.la/category/im-ok/", "https://acid.la/category/acid-magazine/", "https://acid.la/category/jijiji-jajaja/", "https://acid.la/", "javascript:void(0)", "https://acid.la/category/espiritualidades/", "https://acid.la/category/tendencixs/", "https://acid.la/category/gaming/", "https://acid.la/category/b3-yours3lf/", "https://acid.la/category/showbiz/", "https://acid.la/category/gen-z/", "#", "https://acid.la/category/techhhh/", "https://acid.la/category/actualidad/", "https://acid.la/category/kulture/", "https://acid.la/category/im-ok/", "https://acid.la/category/acid-magazine/", "https://acid.la/ca